column2:
"It's not enough! Not enough....
My power... is being drained....
How... why is this....?"

"I see!
This is your doing!
You're the reason my power is fading!"

"Damn you!
My power... my body...
It's not enough!"
"You think you have time to be looking around? I said I would cut you down here, didn't I?"
"What's wrong? The you from the past should have been able to easily stand this much pain!"
"If I could just... get my body... back!"

"Hang your head and die with regret!
This is the end for you!"
"Who are you? Judging from this feeling... another Dark Falz!?"
"Damn! Looks like we missed our chance! <%me>, Sara, let's retreat."
